{
  "texts": [
    "In recent years, chatbots' function of interacting with users through human-like languages promotes researchers to explore the methods of using them to meet these EFL learner's requirements.The studies evaluating the effectiveness of providing personalized feedback to learners' speaking exercises through chatbots show optimistic results.",
    "In 2024, Mhasakar et al.",
    "developed an LLM-based application called Comuniqa to transcribe and evaluate user speech inputs.",
    "They observed that the output of Comuniqa is accurate, and it is more helpful than other traditional applications for learners who cannot access human instruction.",
    "However, compared with human experts, AIs cannot provide the same level of emotional support and personalized guidance [7]."
  ]
}